trans-unit.source: Service Request Information required by Support team for troubleshooting Azure Mobile Engagement issues
trans-unit.target: Service Request Information required by Support team for troubleshooting Azure Mobile Engagement issues

trans-unit.source: Provide the following information when you open a service request for any Mobile Engagement service:
trans-unit.target: Provide the following information when you open a service request for any Mobile Engagement service:

trans-unit.source: Name of the API or UI section where the issue occurs
trans-unit.target: Name of the API or UI section where the issue occurs

trans-unit.source: Text of any error message you receive
trans-unit.target: Text of any error message you receive

trans-unit.source: Results of any tests you have performed from the <linkText>Troubleshooting Guides</linkText><title></title>
trans-unit.target: Results of any tests you have performed from the <linkText>Troubleshooting Guides</linkText><title></title>

trans-unit.source: SDK version and platform of your app (Android SDK 2.4.1, iOS 1.16.2, etc.)
trans-unit.target: SDK version and platform of your app (Android SDK 2.4.1, iOS 1.16.2, etc.)

trans-unit.source: Download location of your production app (or the APK/TGZ files of your development app)
trans-unit.target: Download location of your production app (or the APK/TGZ files of your development app)

trans-unit.source: "AndroidManifest.xml" and/or any code snippet from your app related to Azure Mobile Engagement (for advanced troubleshooting)
trans-unit.target: "AndroidManifest.xml" and/or any code snippet from your app related to Azure Mobile Engagement (for advanced troubleshooting)
